            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-slate-900">Operations Autopilot</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6 text-sm">
              A logic layer that handles the dirty work of data entry, scheduling, and logistics without human error.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-500">
                    <Icon name="ph:check-circle" class="text-orange-500" /> Document & PDF Intake
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-500">
                    <Icon name="ph:check-circle" class="text-orange-500" /> Geo-Spatial Dispatching
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-500">
