            <p>
              I founded LogicLoom in New Jersey with a simple philosophy: <strong>Software should be an asset, not a subscription.</strong> I don't just "set up tools"‚ÄîI architect workflows that run your business autonomously, with the same rigorous error handling I use for enterprise clients.
            </p>
            <p>
              I personally oversee every architecture we deploy.
